<br>
Go there and first CoH people with permanent invis skills....like rogues, monks, shadowknights, necromancers, bards.<br>
<br>
Then summon people with fixed duration invis spells....mages, wizards, enchanters.<br>
<br>
Then have everyone else be invis and summon them down too.  That way, when invis breaks, youll have your full team there.  There will be between 4-6 mobs youll have to kill when it does.  Don't forget, people who dont have fixed duration invis can join the bards. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=106710"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.lehigh.edu/~dsf3/EQ/rhionsligo.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> <br>
